                                Cards
                            </a>

                            <a href="#"
                               class="text-cyan-100 hover:bg-cyan-600 hover:text-white group flex items-center rounded-md px-2 py-2 text-base font-medium">
                                <svg class="mr-4 h-6 w-6 flex-shrink-0 text-cyan-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
